## ğŸ“– Usage with MCP Clients

### Claude Desktop

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "discord-py-suite": {
      "command": "uv",
      "args": ["run", "discord-py-suite"],
      "env": {
        "DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN": "your_token_here",
        "ALLOW_GUILD_IDS": "your_guild_id"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

### Direct Python

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "discord-py-suite": {
      "command": "python",
      "args": ["-m", "discord_py_suite"],
      "env": {
        "DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN": "your_token_here"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

